A class ThreadDemo stores a thread name and an array of Strings. Constructor accepts the name of the thread and size of the array .It then creates the array with the given size and reads the elements of the array. The  thread displays “thread-name starts” and then it display all the string one by one .Write a program to create two threads of the class, one of them display the days of week and the other displays  the months of the years. The main thread should also display “main thread active when it gets the timeslice.
